paragraphs.text: I so love this, Tre! If I had a girl, I would do the same exact thing. Not the details because I don’t have the brothers for the uncles, but I’d shower her with unlimited love and expose her to all great writers, artists and musicians. I’d encourage her to find out who she is in the depths of her spirit and no matter who that is I would support her and respect her. Ah, if I had a girl…

1c3c0d53ad6c.title: I have a girl: she’s 24 now.

paragraphs.text: I have a girl: she’s 24 now. She’s turned out to be a smart, beautiful young lady with a good heart. You just do the best you can to teach them how to be a good person, and hope it makes a dent. One thing I do know: I limited TV and video games very early on, but the one thing I NEVER said no to was books. Best thing I ever did. She is still a…
